      <b data-is-speakable>Lindy West Says 'The Witches Are Coming' — And They Are Rightfully Angry</b>   <b data-is-speakable>"For a long time, a certain set of men have called women like me 'witches' to silence and discredit us," West says. Her book explores misogyny, the #MeToo movement and growing up female in America.</b>
